Name: Devereax Point
Description: Consistent reef point break easily accessable from anywhere in Isla Vista and a steady flow of waves

Name: Campus Point
Description: Easy point break located right on the UCSB campus swell magnent great for beginners

Name: Rincon
Description: World-class point break 20 minutes south of Santa Barbara, always crowded but the best wave on this stretch of coeast

Name: El Capitan
Description: Sketchy rocky point that breaks shallow if your not local it will be hard to get waves.

Name: Sandspit
Description: Rare breaking beach break in downtown santa barbara that produces some of the best barrells in the area

Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!
